    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">Including works dealing with two or more of the fine arts media, i.e. literature, performing arts (dance, motion pictures, music, opera, theater) or the visual arts</skos:scopeNote>
    <skos:editorialNote xml:lang="en">Works on any one of these subjects are classified with the subject in classes GV, M, N, P, TR</skos:editorialNote>
